## 5. TECH STACK — Replace marquee with a grid

The scrolling ticker for tech stack feels like a repeat of the manifesto marquee. Two scrolling elements on the same page is one too many. Replace with a static grid that feels more technical and intentional.

Design: A dark section (black background) with tech labels arranged in a clean grid. Each tech is a "terminal tag" — monospace, bordered, but static. Some are highlighted (primary stack) and some are dimmer (secondary tools).

```
